{"tid":269261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<中時已删除>蔡政府批六四 國台辦:只有大陸人民才有發言權","createTime":"2017-06-03T15:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T10:21:55.000Z","uid":35790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f57e566b032529e849d60154de102c03f8c51fa1","tid":269261,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:39:41.000Z","msg":"蔡政府批六四 國台辦:只有大陸人民才有發言權<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170603005174-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170603005174-260407&d=LFPffSP%2B5dJGqMzEehvWeb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=32a25309\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170603005174-260407</a> &lt;中時已删除&gt;<br />\n備份一下 頁面已經被刪掉了 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zGojISI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzGojISI.png&h=e10003c3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dSEignj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdSEignj.png&h=aa6082a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全文<br />\n台灣ptt文章網址: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1496501927.A.73C.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1496501927.A.73C.html&d=LFPffSP%2B5dJGqMzEehvWeb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=66d686b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1496501927.A.73C.html</a>"},{"pid":"9ce1d8193d34f385e45cd671dabd3a1a8c64b02e","tid":269261,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊一國"},{"pid":"62fbebadddccd72354efa9b80c7dce4f7eda23e5","tid":269261,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"回應蔡政府「六四」聲明 國台辦：大陸人民才有發言權<br />\n<br />\n2017-06-03 23:13聯合報 記者林庭瑤╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n今年適逢六四事件28周年，陸委會、民進黨連發聲明，指中國大陸應省思「六四事件」重要歷史啟示，真正落實民主化及人權保障。<span style=\"color: red;\">大陸國台辦發言人馬曉光今天（6月3日）指出，大陸政治經濟社會發展情況，只有大陸人民才最有發言權</span>。<br />\n<br />\n馬曉光回應媒體提問表示，在中國共產黨領導下，中國特色社會主義事業取得舉世矚目的成就，政治、經濟、社會、文化、生態文明建設全面推進，人民生活水準大幅改善，國際地位和影響顯著提升。我們比歷史上任何時期都更接近中華民族偉大復興的目標。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，事實證明，大陸所走的中國特色社會主義道路，是歷史的必然、人民的選擇，符合最廣大人民的根本利益，得到人民群眾的衷心擁護，也越來越受到世界的尊重。我們對未來充滿信心。<br />\n<br />\n馬曉光強調，「大陸政治經濟社會發展情況，只有大陸人民才最有發言權。」至於台灣政府和民進黨推行其理念與價值觀給台灣社會帶來的亂象與傷害，相信台灣民眾會有切身感受和判斷。<br />\n<br />\n馬曉光表示，台灣政府和民進黨應該深刻反思造成台灣社會天怒人怨及當前兩岸關係陷入僵局的原因何在，而不是轉移焦點、推卸責任，進一步煽動兩岸對立，破壞兩岸關係。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/2502677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F2502677&d=LFPffSP%2B5dJGqMzEehvWeb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=67b00d3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/2502677</a><br />\n香港班大中華膠64晚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be660829f7142573d7485c45897fb9ed197822e9","tid":269261,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"證明香港唔理係正確"},{"pid":"393771bfe3bb82ab0131d0e17714ed09db018d34","tid":269261,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明香港唔理係正確</blockquote><br />\n只有中國人才有發言權"},{"pid":"83d003b183a92879f69cec2181cc1f7ad54c3b9a","tid":269261,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:09:21.000Z","msg":"歡慶六四屠殺為支那搵到最適合走既道路"},{"pid":"47259648b8159b1ed204be7a3a69419bb2bc6e6c","tid":269261,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"最大的台獨份子係國台辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183062b5a377ab9e3655c0815944918dfd8050a6","tid":269261,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"只有大陸人民才能有發言權<br />\n但大陸從來都冇發言權"},{"pid":"b613b7f1ba2f7231a5309372fe14715309c16510","tid":269261,"uid":92301,"l